articles.title: Roque loses bid for International Law Commission seat - Philstar.com
articles.description: Presidential spokesperson failed to clinch a seat at the International Law Commission, garnering the least number of votes among 11 candidates from Asia-Pacific states for the eight seats available on the panel for representatives coming from the region.
